title: Open concept - Large One Bedroom
posting_body: This apartment is located in the heart of Capitol Hill!
Enjoy easy access to I-5 & I-90, lots of restaurants, grocery stores, and shopping.
Just a short distance to downtown Seattle and many schools including Seattle University, Cornish, and Seattle Central College.
Entry: Large closet, with plank wood flooring and recessed lights.
The living room is carpeted and has large windows overlooking city scape from the 3rd floor with a deck to enjoy the scenery .
This kitchen has plank style wood floors and is a u shape, with lots of cabinetry and counter space.
Also offers a cute bar top counter space.
Updated appliances, along with energy efficient fixtures.
The bathroom is spacious with a great vanity, full tub and shower.
The bedroom has ample space for Queen or King size bed and has a large closet.
